Thanks to your brave assault on the orbital fortress, we were able to acquire the cult's protected data.
The lair of the Yellow Father has been located.
On a vulcanic planet far, far away, there is a monastery chiseled inside a mountain...
This will be your hardest battle.
All our hope rests in you. The fate of the galaxy is in your hands.
Succeed, or else we will be sentenced to joyless lives of asceticism, renunciation, and sexual abstinence.

You have put an end to many of my apprentices. Thank you for that! Since they proved so weak, I wouldn't have had much use for them anyway.
Your journey ends here.
